					    <h1>
                            &#8220;Fascism is rising in America&#8221;: The Koch brothers and democracy&#8217;s dispiriting demise                        </h1>

					    <h2>
                            We're still paying the price for Citizens United, and our oligarchs are poised to capture even more political power                        </h2>

					    <span class="byline"><a href='http://www.salon.com/writer/thom_hartmann/' rel='author' class="gaTrackLinkEvent" data-ga-track-json="[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;click&quot;, &quot;Thom Hartmann&quot;]" >Thom Hartmann</a>, AlterNet</span>

