                <h4>13 of "Girls'" most cringeworthy sex scenes</h4>
                <p class='slideTitle'>Shoshanna and Ray, "Together" </p>
                <p>As Shoshanna and Ray near the end of their relationship, we can see their sexual chemistry getting worse and worse. It’s no more evident than when Ray is penetrating a clothed and visibly horrified Shoshanna from behind, who ends the encounter by asking if her partner will just “get out of me.” </p>
                
                
            </div>
        </li><li class="slide">        <script type="json/config" class="jsonConfig scrollTrack">
