            <div class='content'>
                
                <h4>13 of "Girls'" most cringeworthy sex scenes</h4>
                <p class='slideTitle'>Marnie and Desi, "Iowa" </p>
                <p>Who gets her butt motorboated? Is this a real thing? Aside from the questionable logistics and reality of Marnie and Desi’s analingus scene, there’s also the awkward moment when Marnie confuses her partner’s declaration of love for licking her butthole with love for her. Oh, Marnie. </p>
                
                
            </div>
        </li><li class="slide">        <script type="json/config" class="jsonConfig scrollTrack">
