            <div class='content'>
                
                <h4>13 of "Girls'" most cringeworthy sex scenes</h4>
                <p class='slideTitle'>Hannah and Adam, "Vagina Panic"  </p>
                <p>There is too much in this scene to dissect: fantasies of an 11-year-old girl with a Cabbage Patch lunchbox, excessive references to that little girl as a “slut” and Adam ripping off a condom to ejaculate on Hannah’s chest. No wonder it ends with Hannah saying she <em>almost</em> came. 
</p>
                
                
